#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Some thrift stores sell by weight. Odoo’s POS can connect with scales to price goods\n"
"            dynamically by weight, ensuring transparency and accuracy."
msgstr ""
"ຮ້ານຂາຍເຄື່ອງມືສອງບາງແຫ່ງຂາຍຕາມນ້ຳໜັກ. Odoo POS ສາມາດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບຊິງຊັ່ງເພື່ອຕັ້ງລາຄາຕາມນ້ຳໜັກໂດຍກົ"
"ງ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ໝັ້ນໃຈໃນຄວາມໂປ່ງໃສ ແລະ ຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model:planning.role,name:thrift_store.planning_role_1
